mber">51</span><br><span class="line-number">52</span><br></div></div><h3 id="_7-字典" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_7-字典" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 7. 字典</h3>
<p>储存的是[键，值]，键名用来查询特定元素，也称作映射、符号表或者关联数组。</p>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token comment">// 检查一个键是否在字典中</span>
